#message:01:000
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star][Wave]Hohohohoho![/fx] [BR]
	[Pause 5]Young man, I knew you were[BR]
	the one the moment I laid[BR]
	eyes on you.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Your fightings skills are beyond[BR]
	any I've witnessed in my long[BR]
	years of parliament.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:001
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]I knew you could do it! [HEART][BR]
	[Pause 10]You were able to kick your[BR]
	addiction and beat it, Mario![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	You've been looking like a much[BR]
	healthier man recently.[BR]
	I'm proud of you. [HEART][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Now don't go picking it back up[BR]
	either, ya hear?[BR]
	[Pause 10]I don't want to see you risking[BR]
	your health for nothing![Wait][End]
}

#message:01:002
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Countless nights I stood in fear[BR]
	that my role as a [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Deity[RestoreColor] [BR]
	would be frowned upon.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I've done such a terrible job.[BR]
	[Pause 5]I was helpless against Bower's[BR]
	merciless influence.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Thanks to you, my friend,[Pause 3] I can[BR]
	firmly say I was wrong for even[BR]
	thinking that way.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I don't regret assisting you to[BR]
	help take back the [SaveColor][Color:1F]Rod of Lust[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Pause 10]I want to prove myself useful[BR]
	to the rest of my comrades.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:003
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Being a corporeal deity as[BR]
	opposed to a spiritual one has[BR]
	never felt better,[Pause 2] man.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Maybe us [SaveColor][Color:22]Love Deities[RestoreColor] can take[BR]
	action more often now and not[BR]
	have to worry about breaching[BR]
	the flow of reality.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[PrintRising]Oh yeah![BR]
	[Pause 5]Watching over love[HEART] and peace[BR]
	just got a whole lot better![Wait][End]
}

#message:01:004
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]I guess I owe you one for saving[BR]
	me back in that volcano, huh?[BR]
	[Pause 10]Well, well, well...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I just might have to take a look[BR]
	at my messages. [HEART][BR]
	[Pause 10]I think a certain Goomba has[BR]
	been messaging me non-stop.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I'm truly grateful![BR]
	[Pause 10][PrintRising]There, I said it![/fx][BR]
	[Pause 5]Don't let it get to your head,[BR]
	you[Shake] big stupid idiot![/fx][Wait][End]
}

#message:01:005
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Erm. Yes, all according to plan.[BR]
	[Pause 10]It theems you two have actually[BR]
	listened to my advice.[BR]
	[Pause 10][Wave]Applause for that, friends.[/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Not just you two.[BR]
	[Pause 5]The rest of your friends are all[BR]
	going to have exceptional lives [BR]
	from now on.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Consider it a personal blessing[BR]
	from the [SaveColor][Color:22]Love Deities[RestoreColor] themselves.[BR]
	[Pause 10]It's the least we could do for[BR]
	helping us restore balance.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	May love find you one day, my[BR]
	good friends! [STAR][Wait][End]
}

#message:01:006
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]You have done an exzellent[BR]
	job, ja?[BR]
	[Pause 5]Your names vill go down in [Wave]Historie[/fx][BR]
	for helping ze [SaveColor][Color:22]Love Deities[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I have learned to be more loyal[BR]
	to mein Kameraden... [Pause 10]My friends.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I retract mein statements about[BR]
	using ze [SaveColor][Color:1F]Rod of Lust[RestoreColor] für evil.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Under nein circumstances should[BR]
	ze Rod be used für malice.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:007
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Ahhh, and Xing![BR]
	[Pause 5]On behalf of all of [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Heaven[RestoreColor],[BR]
	I'd like the [SaveColor][Color:04]Chinese Republic of[BR]
	Stars[RestoreColor] to unite with us.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	With the vigour of faith combined[BR]
	with the might of military and[BR]
	knowledge, the [SaveColor][Color:1F]Rod of Lust[RestoreColor] will[BR]
	be forever held safely.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:008
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Wow... [Pause 10]I'm... [Pause 10]I'm not sure how to[BR]
	respond to that.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I'll have to talk it through with my[BR]
	boss and see what he says.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	This is perhaps a once in a life[BR]
	time opportunity for both [SaveColor][Color:22]Love[BR]
	Heaven[RestoreColor] and the [SaveColor][Color:04]Chinese Republic[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	As a matter of a fact, I[BR]
	wholeheartedly approve of this[BR]
	union proposal.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	It was a blast working with you[BR]
	guys... [Pause 15]even if you weren't aware[BR]
	of it most of the time.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:009
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star][PrintRising][Pause 5]Hoho![/fx][BR]
	[Pause 10]With the work and dedication you[BR]
	have provided to your company,[Pause 10][BR]
	I simply doubt he'll decline.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Alas, we have waffled for long[BR]
	enough, I'm afraid.[BR]
	[Pause 10]It's time to resume our overseeing[BR]
	in [SaveColor][Color:22]Love Heaven[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Down 4][Size 24][SizeWave]Farewell...[BR]
	      and until then...[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:00A
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Welp, that settles that now,[BR]
	doesn't it?[BR]
	[Pause 10]I have to report back to my[BR]
	boss about the operation.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	The[SaveColor][Color:04] Chinese Republic[RestoreColor] being a[BR]
	part of [SaveColor][Color:22]Love Heaven[RestoreColor] is a massive[BR]
	deal, after all.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Life is going to be incredible[BR]
	again thanks to our combined[BR]
	efforts![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	It may have sucked when Bower[BR]
	was in power[Pause 10] and hey,[Pause 10] depending[BR]
	on who you ask,[Pause 8] it may have[BR]
	sucked before that![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	The point is,[Pause 5] we're going to[BR]
	make sure everyone can have[BR]
	an equal shot at finding the[BR]
	one they will love.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:00B
{
	[Style Right]
	You've matured so much since[BR]
	I got the chance to work with[BR]
	you, Xing.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	You started out perverted and[BR]
	devious,[Pause 15] but over time, you really[BR]
	proved how much of a hard-worker[BR]
	you can truly be.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	We'll be sure to pray to you[BR]
	every week here at Doki Doki[BR]
	Castle, Xing.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:00C
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Sniff...[BR]
	[Pause 10][Wait][Yield][Next]
	[Pause 10]Ahem! You didn't see anything.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I'm glad you'll always remember[BR]
	what I did for you.[BR]
	[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:00D
{
	[Style Right]
	Wowie zowie! Bro![BR]
	And you did all that without[BR]
	my help, huh?[BR]
	[Pause 5][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Think about all those times I[BR]
	turned you into a ball and[BR]
	Hammered you at the enemy?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	We could have done some cool[BR]
	Bros. Moves, bro.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Oh well,[Pause 10] it seems your Goomba[BR]
	friend and your other pals are[BR]
	more important than your brother[BR]
	Luigi, huh?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Well, bro, one day I'm-a gonna[BR]
	have my [SizeWave]OWN[/fx] adventure and [Pause 3]YOU[Pause 3][BR]
	are not invited![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I could be off saving the day[BR]
	and being the green hero I am,[Pause 10][BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:03]Luigi[RestoreColor]![BR]
	[Wait][End]
}

