	[Style Right]
	[Down 8][Size 32]Yo,[Pause 6] Goombarius![Wait][End]
}

#message:01:010
{
	[Style Right]
	Parakarius?[BR]
	[Pause 10]What are you doing here?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Did Goompapa order something[BR]
	for his carpentry?  [Wait][End]
}

#message:01:011
{
	[Style Right]
	No, no. That ain't it.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Actually...[Pause 3] I think the sender[BR]
	wanted to remain anonymous.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	But uh...[BR]
	[Pause 10]There [Wave]iiiissss[/fx] some lipstick on[BR]
	the letter.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:012
{
	[Style Right]
	[PrintRising]Ew![/fx][Pause 10][PrintRising] Parakarius, why the heck[BR]
	would you do that?[/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Pause 10]You're gonna get in a lot of[BR]
	trouble if your boss finds out[BR]
	you've been making out with the[BR]
	letters![Pause 15] You freak![Wait][End]
}

#message:01:013
{
	[Style Right]
	[Shake][PrintRising]No no no no![/fx][/fx][BR]
	[PrintRising]It wasn't me![/fx][BR]
