	That's...[Pause 10] what the letter was[BR]
	like when it was submitted to[BR]
	the office...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Ummm.....[Pause 20] [PrintGrowing]Goombarius?[/fx][BR]
	[Pause 15]Perhaps you have someone in your[BR]
	life that I don't know about?[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:014
{
	[Style Right]
