}

#message:01:01F
{
	[Style Right]
	[PrintGrowing]Ahem...[/fx] [Pause 10]Kolorado, I think you[BR]
	have a bit of explaining to do.[BR]
	[Pause 15]Don't think I haven't caught you[BR]
	stealing packages.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	One of your colleagues in[BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:05]Koopa Village[RestoreColor] submitted a[BR]
