#message:01:022
{
	[Style Right]
	Hey, bro, guess what?[BR]
	[Pause 10]You heard that[SaveColor][Color:22] Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor]'s[BR]
	back in the center of Kinoko Town?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	That's-a great news![BR]
	[Pause 5]They're even holding a ceremony[BR]
