#message:01:042
{
	[Style Right]
	Ara ara~[BR]
	[Pause 5]The princess of[SaveColor][Color:09] Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor][BR]
	asked me personally to make[BR]
	beautiful baskets of flowers. [HEART][BR]
