}

#message:01:044
{
	[Style Right]
	I say [Pause 3]"[SaveColor][Color:00]Don't come back![RestoreColor]"[Pause 3] all the[BR]
	time,[Pause 3] but this time I think I need[BR]
	to get a slightly different message[BR]
	across this time.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[PrintRising]"Don't come here at all!"[/fx][BR]
	[Pause 15]It's a holiday, jackass, so the[BR]
	inn is completely closed.[BR]
	[Pause 5]No loitering.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:045
{
	[Style Right]
