#message:01:066
{
	[Style Right]
	Thank you everyone for coming[BR]
	to Doki Doki Castle today.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	We're glad to be reopening the[BR]
	church to allow everyone of all[BR]
	races and gender to participate[BR]
	in worshipping our gods.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	The Love Deities are our guiding[BR]
	moonlight.[Pause 15] Without them, we'd be[BR]
	lost in our unbridled search for[BR]
	care and romance.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:067
{
	[Style Right]
	Thanks to the efforts of many,[BR]
	the evil fiend Bower has been[BR]
	taken down and [PrintRising]banished to hell[/fx][BR]
	for his wrongdoings.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	With the [SaveColor][Color:1F]Rod of Lust[RestoreColor] safely in[BR]
	the care of our new alliance,[BR]
	[Pause 5]the [SaveColor][Color:04]Chinese Republic of Stars[RestoreColor],[BR]
	our forces are invincible.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:068
{
	[Style Right]
	No longer will you all have to[BR]
	suffer with cloudy nights and[BR]
	intoxicating fog across the land.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	The Love Deities will be supplying[BR]
	us with love-refreshened air to[BR]
	support thousands of innocent [BR]
	lives.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:069
{
	[Style Right]
	All of you will prosper in a[BR]
	stress-free age of freedom and[BR]
	sentimentality.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I believe[Pause 5] that love is created[BR]
	equally and is a righteous feeling[BR]
	that everyone deserves to[BR]
	experience.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Whether they be good heart[BR]
	[Pause 5]or evil heart,[Pause 5] love can be[BR]
	expressed in a multitude of ways.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:06A
{
	[Style Right]
	For those of you who know[BR]
	someone who is of evil heart,[BR]
	[Pause 10]I implore you to sit down and[BR]
	persuade with them kindness.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	After all, the only way to undo[BR]
	a negative mind is to cure it[BR]
	with your overflowing positivity.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	That positivity will spread[BR]
	happiness around you and make[BR]
	our world [PrintRising]a better place[/fx]![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	That is what[Wave] I[/fx][Pause 6] and many others[BR]
	[Pause 3]have experienced first-hand[BR]
	praying at[SaveColor][Color:09] Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor] for[BR]
	many decades.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:06B
{
	[Style Right]
	After being held captive for so[BR]
	long in Bower's chambers, I had[BR]
	the help of a kind acquaintance...[BR]
	[Pause 20]A friend, I might even say.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Xing,[Pause 2] if you're out there...[BR]
	[Pause 10]I know you're doing good things[BR]
	for the sake of your Chinese[BR]
	agency...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	As well as us and even the[BR]
	Love Deities themselves.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:06C
{
	[Style Right]
	He made me realize my important[BR]
	role as the crown princess of[BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:22]Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Prior to that, I had lost my[BR]
	memory as to who I even was,[Pause 10] but[BR]
	it was thanks to him that he was[BR]
	able to unearth my identity.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:06D
{
	[Style Right]
	This Mushroom Kingdom of ours...[BR]
	[Pause 10]Let's cherish it for what we[BR]
	have and not what we don't.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I swear I will do what I can to[BR]
	make this kingdom great again.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Everyone deserves it.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	My absence is inexcusable,[BR]
	helpless as I was.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I will stand up for all of you and[BR]
	ensure you live happy lives.[Wait][End]
}

#message:01:06E
{
	[Style Right]
	And...[BR]
	[Pause 5]There's a certain individual I[BR]
	would like to see in my chambers[BR]
	after the ceremony is over.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
